Actor Junior Pope Odonwodo has revealed the promise he made to himself before becoming a celebrity. He explained that when he started out in the industry, it was difficult for celebrities to consent to taking photos with fans. He said he vowed that once he becomes a celebrity, he will never hesitate to oblige fans who want to take pictures with him. He made this known while posing for photographs with his fans. See below. A post shared by Lindaikejiblog (@lindaikejiblogofficial)